'''Rugir-e Qaleh Hajji''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0631><U+0648><U+06AF><U+064A><U+0631><U+0642><U+0644><U+0639><U+0647> <U+062D><U+0627><U+062C><U+064A>}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''R<U+016B>g<U+012B>r-e Qal<U+2018>eh <U+1E28><U+0101>jj<U+012B>'''; also known as '''R<U+016B>g<U+012B>r-e Qal<U+2018>eh <U+2019><U+0101>jj<U+012B>''')<ref>{{GEOnet3|-3746110|Rugir-e Qaleh Hajji}}</ref> is a village in [[Kheyrgu Rural District]], [[Ala-e Marvdasht District]], [[Lamerd County]], [[Fars Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 173, in 41 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|07}}</ref>  

